channel.title: No Swim Zone
channel.itunes:subtitle: A podcast about male infertility and men's mental health
channel.itunes:author: Sean Tuck
channel.itunes:summary: Follow me as I deal with my infertility and my wife and I navigate infertility treatment. We share our story of male infertility and the stories of others, to support men and women going through their own infertility struggles.
